{
  "stem": "6258.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if he didn't, he probably would be much more safe than instead when he came back, because then he was in ghetto with us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then he was in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then he was in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when he went to Dachau, from where-- because before they were sent to Dachau, they were sent to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was already 19-- 1945.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was maybe March, and they were dragged all around and around.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was such a skeleton that when they came to registration, there was a Polish priest, who-- also an inmate, who was registering them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when he noticed such a young guy like my brother and his friend, he right away told them, I give you two minutes to find a Polish name.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so my brother become, from Nelken, [INAUDIBLE], and that other become [INAUDIBLE] from [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Oris. ?] And this saved their life because, unfortunately, the rest of that whole transport went straight to death.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they survive by pretty, a wonder, miracle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, boy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, first of all, the day began with [INAUDIBLE] my nanny, who was up till [INAUDIBLE] and was trying to make me eat my breakfast, which I didn't, and I didn't want it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, well, I went to school, and then I came back home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At 1 o'clock, we had a beautiful dinner all together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My brother was eating everything in sight, but I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I was making homework, and nobody was complaining about homework.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe we didn't like it very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But as a matter of fact, I like it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I went for a walk with my nanny or with my mother or this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then parents went to see their friends in cafe or this or that.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
